column7: A comprehensive and in-depth survey of commodity price analysis with emphasis on the fundamental factors affecting prices of agricultural products; sources of information relating to production and demand factors; government activities as they relate to prices of agricultural products; technical analysis of agricultural product prices; and market efficiency and forecasting. 3 undergraduate hours. 3 graduate hours. Prerequisite: ACE 100 or ECON 102; ACE 261, or equivalent.
column9: 3 undergraduate hours. 3 graduate hours. Prerequisite: ACE 100 or ECON 102; ACE 261, or equivalent.
